{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/absolute-middle-center/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"id":"274b01b8-85e5-5f40-858c-94362f374650","title":"「高さ分からない要素」をCSS（absolute）で上下左右中央揃えにする方法","slug":"absolute-middle-center","content":"<p>要素の高さを意識せずに上下中央に揃える方法を紹介します。</p>\n<p>レスポンシブで要素の大きさが固定できない今の時代に合った指定の仕方だと思うので、ぜひ覚えてください！</p>\n<p><code>position: abosolute</code>を使います。</p>\n<div class=\"chat\"><figure class=\"chat-img\"><img src=\"https://haniwaman.com/wp-content/themes/hpcode/img/haniwa.png\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>はにわまん</figcaption></figure><div class=\"chat-content\">absoluteとtransformの組み合わせはめっちゃ使ってます！</div></div>\n<div id=\"toc_container\" class=\"no_bullets\"><p class=\"toc_title\">目次</p><ul class=\"toc_list\"><li><a href=\"#i\"><span class=\"toc_number toc_depth_1\">1</span> 上下揃え</a></li><li><a href=\"#i-2\"><span class=\"toc_number toc_depth_1\">2</span> 左右揃え</a></li><li><a href=\"#i-3\"><span class=\"toc_number toc_depth_1\">3</span> 上下左右揃え</a></li><li><a href=\"#i-4\"><span class=\"toc_number toc_depth_1\">4</span> おわり</a></li></ul></div>\n<h2><span id=\"i\">上下揃え</span></h2>\n<div class=\"absolute-parent\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 300px; background: #00BCD4;\">\n<div class=\"absolute-middle\" style=\"color: #fff\">上下の真ん中</div>\n</div>\n<pre><span class=\"code-copy\" data-clipboard-target=\"#code-0\">コピー</span><code id=\"code-0\" class=\"html\">&lt;div class=\"absolute-parent\"&gt;\r\n\t&lt;div class=\"absolute-middle\"&gt;上下の真ん中&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>\n<pre><span class=\"code-copy\" data-clipboard-target=\"#code-1\">コピー</span><code id=\"code-1\" class=\"css\">.absolute-parent {\r\n  position: relative;\r\n  width: 100%;\r\n  height: 300px;\r\n  background: #00BCD4;\r\n}\r\n.absolute-middle {\r\n  position: absolute;\r\n  top: 50%;\r\n  transform: translateY(-50%);\r\n  color: #fff\r\n}\r\n</code></pre>\n<h2><span id=\"i-2\">左右揃え</span></h2>\n<div class=\"absolute-parent\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 300px; background: #00BCD4;\">\n<div class=\"absolute-center\" style=\"color: #fff\">左右の真ん中</div>\n</div>\n<pre><span class=\"code-copy\" data-clipboard-target=\"#code-2\">コピー</span><code id=\"code-2\" class=\"html\">&lt;div class=\"absolute-parent\"&gt;\r\n\t&lt;div class=\"absolute-center\"&gt;左右の真ん中&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>\n<pre><span class=\"code-copy\" data-clipboard-target=\"#code-3\">コピー</span><code id=\"code-3\" class=\"css\">.absolute-parent {\r\n  position: relative;\r\n  width: 100%;\r\n  height: 300px;\r\n  background: #00BCD4;\r\n}\r\n.absolute-center {\r\n  position: absolute;\r\n  left: 50%;\r\n  transform: translateX(-50%);\r\n  color: #fff\r\n}\r\n</code></pre>\n<h2><span id=\"i-3\">上下左右揃え</span></h2>\n<div class=\"absolute-parent\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 300px; background: #00BCD4;\">\n<div class=\"absolute-middle-center\" style=\"color: #fff\">上下左右の真ん中</div>\n</div>\n<pre><span class=\"code-copy\" data-clipboard-target=\"#code-4\">コピー</span><code id=\"code-4\" class=\"html\">&lt;div class=\"absolute-parent\"&gt;\r\n\t&lt;div class=\"absolute-middle-center\"&gt;上下左右の真ん中&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>\n<pre><span class=\"code-copy\" data-clipboard-target=\"#code-5\">コピー</span><code id=\"code-5\" class=\"css\">.absolute-parent {\r\n  position: relative;\r\n  width: 100%;\r\n  height: 300px;\r\n  background: #00BCD4;\r\n}\r\n.absolute-middle-center {\r\n  position: absolute;\r\n  top: 50%;\r\n  left: 50%;\r\n  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\r\n  color: #fff\r\n}\r\n</code></pre>\n<h2><span id=\"i-4\">おわり</span></h2><div class=\"matome\"><div class=\"matome-img\"><img src=\"https://haniwaman.com/wp-content/themes/hpcode/img/haniwa.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"matome-twitter\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/haniwa008?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" class=\"twitter-follow-button\" data-show-screen-name=\"false\" data-size=\"large\" data-lang=\"ja\" data-show-count=\"true\">Follow @haniwa008</a><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></div></div><!-- /matome -->\n<p><code>position: abosolute</code>を使って、上下左右に中央揃えする方法の紹介でした。</p>\n<p>マジで便利でわたしも多用しています。ぜひ、みなさまも使ってみてください！</p>\n","date":"December 24, 2017","categories":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"css"}],"tags":null,"author":{"name":"はにわまん","slug":"haniwaman"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"274b01b8-85e5-5f40-858c-94362f374650"}}}